<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Free CPT Code Finder, Search CPT Codes, wRVUs, and Surgical Billing Guides</title>
<meta name="description" content="Search CPT codes for free, review wRVUs, compare common surgical procedures, and learn modifier, global period, and billing rules with practical guides for surgeons and coders.">
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://freecptcodefinder.com/">
<meta property="og:title" content="Free CPT Code Finder, Search CPT Codes, wRVUs, and Surgical Billing Guides">
<meta property="og:description" content="Search CPT codes for free, review wRVUs, compare common surgical procedures, and learn modifier, global period, and billing rules with practical guides for surgeons and coders.">
<meta property="og:url" content="https://freecptcodefinder.com/">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:site_name" content="Free CPT Code Finder">
<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"WebSite","name":"Free CPT Code Finder","url":"https://freecptcodefinder.com/","description":"Free CPT code lookup and surgical billing education for surgeons, residents, advanced practice clinicians, and coders.","potentialAction":{"@type":"SearchAction","target":"https://freecptcodefinder.com/codes/{search_term_string}.html","query-input":"required name=search_term_string"}},{"@type":"Organization","name":"Free CPT Code Finder","url":"https://freecptcodefinder.com/","logo":"https://freecptcodefinder.com/apple-touch-icon.png"}]}</script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-NPFGH437ZS"></script>
<script>window.dataLayer=window.dataLayer||[];function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}gtag('js',new Date());gtag('config','G-NPFGH437ZS');</script>
<style>
:root{--paper:#FAFAF7;--ink:#0A0A0A;--ink2:#52525B;--ink3:#9A9A94;--line:#E4E4E0;--line2:#CFCCC0;--ox:#6E1919;--ox2:#F4EBEB;--steel:#1E3A5F;--moss:#2D5A3D;--warn:#A8611A;--white:#fff}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html,body{background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
.mono{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',ui-monospace,monospace;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
button,input,select{font:inherit;color:inherit}
button{cursor:pointer;background:none;border:0}
a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}

/* LAYOUT */
.shell{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 420px;min-height:100vh}
@media(max-width:1000px){.shell{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.main{padding:0 40px 48px;border-right:1px solid var(--line)}
@media(max-width:1000px){.main{border-right:0;padding:0 20px 32px}}

/* HEADER */
.hdr{padding:22px 0 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);margin-bottom:32px}
.hdr-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px;margin-bottom:4px}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.mk{width:28px;height:28px;color:var(--ox)}
.title{font-size:22px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;margin-top:2px;margin-left:0}
.sub a{color:var(--ox)}
.hdr-right{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:10px}
.topnav{display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}
.topnav a{color:var(--ink2)}
.topnav a:hover,.topnav a.active{color:var(--ox)}
.meta{display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;align-items:center}
.meta .sep{width:1px;height:10px;background:var(--line2)}
@media(max-width:700px){.hdr-top{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}.hdr-right{align-items:flex-start}.topnav{flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px}}
.live::before{content:"";display:inline-block;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--moss);margin-right:5px;vertical-align:1px;animation:p 1.8s infinite}
@keyframes p{0%,100%{opacity:.35}50%{opacity:1}}

/* SEARCH */
.search-wrap{margin:0 0 40px;position:relative}
.quick-links{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:0 0 16px}
.quick-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:999px;background:var(--white);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink2);letter-spacing:.02em}
.quick-link:hover{border-color:var(--ox);color:var(--ox);background:var(--ox2)}
.search-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;margin-bottom:10px}
.search{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:8px;padding:18px 20px;transition:border-color .15s}
.search:hover,.search:focus-within{border-color:var(--ink)}
.search svg{width:18px;height:18px;color:var(--ink3);flex-shrink:0}
.search input{flex:1;border:0;outline:0;font-size:16px;background:transparent;letter-spacing:-.005em}
.search input::placeholder{color:var(--ink3)}
.kbd{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink2);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 6px;background:var(--paper)}
.autocomplete-results{display:none;position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;margin-top:8px;background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 18px 48px rgba(10,10,10,.08);z-index:20;max-height:420px;overflow:auto}
.autocomplete-results.show{display:block}
.autocomplete-empty{padding:16px 18px;color:var(--ink2);font-size:13px}
.autocomplete-group{padding:8px 0}
.autocomplete-item{padding:12px 18px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);cursor:pointer;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start}
.autocomplete-item:first-child{border-top:0}
.autocomplete-item:hover,.autocomplete-item.active{background:var(--ox2)}
.autocomplete-main{flex:1;min-width:0}
.autocomplete-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--ink)}
.autocomplete-meta{margin-top:3px;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.autocomplete-code{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ox);white-space:nowrap}
.autocomplete-action{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink3);white-space:nowrap;padding-top:1px}

/* SECTIONS */
.sections{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr 1fr;gap:24px}
@media(max-width:900px){.sections{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.sec{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px}
.sec-h{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);margin-bottom:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.sec-h .bdot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:2px}
.sec-h.surg .bdot{background:var(--ox)}
.sec-h.in .bdot{background:var(--warn)}
.sec-h.out .bdot{background:var(--moss)}

/* SPECIALTY ROWS */
.spec{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.spec:last-child{border-bottom:0}
.spec-t{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:12px 2px;cursor:pointer;transition:color .12s}
.spec-t:hover{color:var(--ox)}
.spec-n{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.005em}
.spec-c{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink3);transition:transform .2s}
.spec.open .spec-c{transform:rotate(90deg);color:var(--ox)}
.spec-body{display:none;padding:4px 2px 14px;animation:sl .2s ease-out}
.spec.open .spec-body{display:block}
.spec-note{margin:0 0 10px;padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:10px;background:var(--ox2);font-size:12px;line-height:1.45;color:var(--ink2)}
.spec-note strong{color:var(--ink)}
@keyframes sl{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-4px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.proc{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto auto;gap:10px;align-items:center;padding:7px 8px;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;transition:background .1s;position:relative}
.proc:hover{background:var(--ox2)}
.proc.has-lat{cursor:pointer}
.proc-n{color:var(--ink);overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.proc-c{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ox);font-weight:500}
.proc-w{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2);min-width:36px;text-align:right}
.proc-bi{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--ink3);margin-left:6px;opacity:.6}
.rvu-chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid #F0D9B0;background:#FDF6EC;color:var(--warn);font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;vertical-align:middle}
.rvu-chip::before{content:'!';font-size:9px;line-height:1}
.lat-tray{display:none;grid-column:1/-1;padding:8px 0 4px;margin-top:4px;border-top:1px dashed var(--line);animation:latin .18s ease-out}
.proc.picking .lat-tray{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center}
.proc.picking{background:var(--ox2)}
@keyframes latin{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-3px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.lat-lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-right:4px}
.lat-chip{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:4px;padding:5px 11px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;transition:all .1s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.lat-chip:hover,.lat-chip.kb,.lat-chip.active{border-color:var(--ox);background:var(--ox);color:var(--white)}
.lat-chip .k{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;opacity:.5;border:1px solid currentColor;border-radius:2px;padding:0 3px}
.lat-cancel{margin-left:auto;background:transparent;border:0;color:var(--ink3);font-size:11px;cursor:pointer}
.lat-cancel:hover{color:var(--ox)}
.approach-tray{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;grid-column:1/-1;padding:0 0 6px;margin-top:6px}
.approach-tray .lat-lbl{margin-right:2px}
.bi-note{position:absolute;right:8px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);background:var(--moss);color:#fff;font-size:10px;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .2s;white-space:nowrap;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.bi-note.show{opacity:1}

/* INPATIENT/OUTPATIENT */
.em-group{padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.em-group:last-child{border-bottom:0}
.em-gh{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:-.005em}
.em-levels{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px}
.em-l{background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:5px;padding:6px 10px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink);cursor:pointer;transition:all .1s}
.em-l:hover{border-color:var(--ox);background:var(--ox2);color:var(--ox)}
.em-l .lvl{color:var(--ink3);margin-right:4px}
.em-l:hover .lvl{color:var(--ox)}
.em-l .wr{color:var(--ink3);font-size:10px;margin-left:4px}

/* ===== CASE BUILDER RAIL ===== */
.rail{background:var(--white);padding:24px 28px;position:sticky;top:0;height:100vh;overflow-y:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
@media(max-width:1000px){.rail{position:static;height:auto;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}}
.rh{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;padding-bottom:14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.rt{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--ink3)}
.rm{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2)}
.tot{padding:22px 0 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.tl{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:6px}
.tn{font-size:54px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.035em;line-height:.95;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
.ts{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);margin-top:8px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.lns{padding:14px 0;flex:1;min-height:180px}
.lns-empty{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink3);font-style:italic;padding:16px 0;text-align:center}
.rl{padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);position:relative}
.rl:last-child{border:0}
.rlt{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:3px}
.rk{font-size:9px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--ink3);padding:2px 6px;border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:3px}
.rk.p{color:var(--ox);border-color:var(--ox);background:var(--ox2)}
.rk.em{color:var(--moss);border-color:var(--moss);background:rgba(45,90,61,.06)}
.rcpt{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:500}
.rmd{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--ox);font-weight:500;margin-left:auto}
.mod-edit{display:inline-block;margin-left:6px;padding:1px 6px;border:1px dashed var(--line2);border-radius:3px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);cursor:pointer;transition:all .12s}
.mod-edit:hover{border-color:var(--ox);color:var(--ox);border-style:solid}
.rx{color:var(--ink3);cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;line-height:1;padding:0 4px}
.rx:hover{color:var(--ox)}

.mpick{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(10,10,10,.45);display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:100;animation:fi .15s}
.mpick.open{display:flex}
@keyframes fi{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
.mpick-box{background:var(--white);border-radius:10px;padding:24px 26px;max-width:440px;width:92%;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
.mpick-h{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:4px}
.mpick-t{font-size:16px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:4px}
.mpick-s{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:16px}
.mpick-ncci{font-size:11px;color:var(--warn);background:#FDF6EC;border:1px solid #F0D9B0;border-radius:5px;padding:8px 10px;margin-bottom:14px;display:none}
.mpick-ncci.show{display:block}
.mpick-opts{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:6px;margin-bottom:16px}
.mpick-opt{text-align:left;padding:11px 13px;background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .1s;display:grid;grid-template-columns:52px 1fr;gap:12px;align-items:center}
.mpick-opt:hover,.mpick-opt.hl{border-color:var(--ox);background:var(--ox2)}
.mpick-opt .mk{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ox)}
.mpick-opt.none .mk{color:var(--ink3)}
.mpick-opt .ml{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink)}
.mpick-opt .md{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2);margin-top:1px;line-height:1.35}
.mpick-warn{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2);background:var(--paper);border-left:2px solid var(--warn);padding:8px 10px;margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.5}
.mpick-foot{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}
.mpick-cancel{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink3);background:none;border:0;cursor:pointer;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.mpick-cancel:hover{color:var(--ox)}
.mpick-foot .k{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3)}
.rd{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:4px}
.rw{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between}
.rw .rwl{color:var(--ink3)}
.ctrls{padding:14px 0 10px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.seg{display:inline-flex;border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden}
.seg button{padding:6px 10px;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink2);background:var(--paper);border-right:1px solid var(--line2);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;text-transform:lowercase}
.seg button:last-child{border-right:0}
.seg button.on{background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper)}
.rf{padding-top:12px;display:flex;gap:8px}
.rf button{flex:1;padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:5px;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;transition:all .1s}
.rf button:hover{border-color:var(--ink);color:var(--ink)}
.rf button.danger:hover{border-color:var(--ox);color:var(--ox)}

/* AI ASSISTANT */
.ai-launch{position:fixed;right:22px;bottom:22px;z-index:120;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:999px;background:var(--ox);color:var(--white);box-shadow:0 18px 36px rgba(10,10,10,.18);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.ai-launch:hover{background:#541212}
.ai-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#9EE6B0}
.ai-panel{position:fixed;right:22px;bottom:84px;width:380px;max-width:calc(100vw - 24px);height:560px;max-height:calc(100vh - 120px);background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 24px 64px rgba(10,10,10,.18);z-index:130;display:none;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}
.ai-panel.open{display:flex}
.ai-head{padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;background:var(--paper)}
.ai-head-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.ai-head-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2);margin-top:3px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;line-height:1.45}
.ai-close{color:var(--ink3);font-size:18px;padding:0 4px}
.ai-close:hover{color:var(--ox)}
.ai-messages{flex:1;overflow:auto;padding:16px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--paper),#fff 35%)}
.ai-msg{margin-bottom:12px;max-width:92%}
.ai-msg.user{margin-left:auto}
.ai-bubble{border-radius:12px;padding:12px 13px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;border:1px solid var(--line)}
.ai-msg.bot .ai-bubble{background:var(--white);color:var(--ink)}
.ai-msg.user .ai-bubble{background:var(--ox);color:var(--white);border-color:var(--ox)}
.ai-meta{margin-top:4px;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.ai-suggest{padding:12px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;background:var(--white)}
.ai-chip{padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:999px;background:var(--paper);font-size:11px;color:var(--ink2)}
.ai-chip:hover{border-color:var(--ox);color:var(--ox);background:var(--ox2)}
.ai-compose{padding:14px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--white)}
.ai-compose textarea{width:100%;min-height:84px;max-height:160px;resize:vertical;border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 13px;background:var(--paper);outline:none}
.ai-compose textarea:focus{border-color:var(--ox);background:var(--white)}
.ai-actions{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:10px;gap:10px}
.ai-note{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;line-height:1.4}
.ai-send{padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--ox);color:var(--white);font-weight:600}
.ai-send:hover{background:#541212}
@media(max-width:700px){.ai-launch{right:14px;left:14px;justify-content:center;bottom:14px}.ai-panel{right:12px;left:12px;bottom:72px;width:auto;height:70vh;max-height:none}}
</style><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"Organization","name":"FreeCPTCodeFinder.com","url":"https://freecptcodefinder.com/","publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"CYRIONYX"}},{"@type":"WebSite","name":"FreeCPTCodeFinder.com","url":"https://freecptcodefinder.com/"},{"@type":"Person","name":"Graydon Stallard","honorificSuffix":"DO, FACOS, FACS","jobTitle":"Surgeon; Founder and Author of FreeCPTCodeFinder.com","knowsAbout":["General Surgery","Surgical Critical Care","Trauma","CPT coding education","surgical documentation"],"url":"https://freecptcodefinder.com/authors/graydon-stallard-do.html"}]}</script></head><body>

<div class="shell">
<main class="main">

<header class="hdr">
<div class="hdr-top">
<div>
<div class="logo">
<svg class="mk" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M6 6l20 20M11 6h15v15"/><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2.5"/></svg>
<div>
<div class="title">Free CPT Code Finder</div>
<div class="sub" style="margin-left:0"><a href="/codes/">CPT lookup</a> · wRVUs · modifiers · billing guides</div>
</div>
</div>
<h1 style="font-size:32px;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin-top:20px;max-width:920px">Find CPT Codes for Case Logs, and Learn the Coding Behind Them</h1>
<p style="margin-top:12px;max-width:860px;color:var(--ink2);font-size:15px">FreeCPTCodeFinder.com helps medical students, residents, fellows, and early-career clinicians quickly look up CPT codes for clinical case logging while learning the RVUs, modifiers, global periods, billing basics, and documentation concepts they will use as attendings.</p>
<div class="quick-links" style="margin-top:18px">
<a class="quick-link" href="/codes/">Search CPT Codes</a>
<a class="quick-link" href="/blog/">Browse Coding Guides</a>
<a class="quick-link" href="/blog/modifiers/modifier-25-explained.html">Modifier 25 guide</a>
<a class="quick-link" href="/blog/modifiers/modifier-59-explained.html">Modifier 59 guide</a>
<a class="quick-link" href="/blog/guides/global-surgical-package-explained.html">Global package guide</a>
<a class="quick-link" href="/blog/rvu/understanding-work-rvus.html">wRVU guide</a>
</div>
<p style="margin-top:10px;max-width:860px;color:var(--ink2);font-size:13px">Built by a trauma surgeon to make case logging and surgical coding education faster, clearer, and easier to verify against official AMA, CMS, payer, and program requirements.</p>
</div>
